1
00:02:04,035 --> 00:02:06,402
- DAMN HIM TO HELL.

2
00:02:17,535 --> 00:02:20,068
[CHATTER]

3
00:02:24,402 --> 00:02:27,502
- HEY, WE FOUND SOME SAKE
OVER HERE, CHIEF.

4
00:02:27,535 --> 00:02:31,235
- WENCH, STAND UP
AND POUR THE CHIEF A DRINK.

5
00:02:39,068 --> 00:02:42,702
- YOU'VE WEAKENED CONSIDERABLY,
HALF-DEMON.

6
00:02:42,735 --> 00:02:43,835
SERVES YOU RIGHT--

7
00:02:43,868 --> 00:02:48,068
SIDING WITH HUMANS
AND MEDDLING IN MY AFFAIRS.

8
00:02:49,202 --> 00:02:50,068
- WE'RE IN TROUBLE.

9
00:02:50,102 --> 00:02:53,068
THE BARRIER
ISN'T GONNA HOLD MUCH LONGER.

10
00:02:54,235 --> 00:02:56,068
- DAMN.

11
00:02:57,468 --> 00:03:03,302
- ATTEND TO THE CHIEF,
YOU FOOLISH WENCH!

12
00:03:03,335 --> 00:03:04,802
[GASPS]

13
00:03:04,835 --> 00:03:06,035
[LAUGHS]

14
00:03:06,068 --> 00:03:08,835
- ARE YOU AFRAID, WOMAN?

15
00:03:08,868 --> 00:03:11,668
SUCH A LOVELY COUNTENANCE.

16
00:03:26,435 --> 00:03:27,735
[SCREAMING]

17
00:03:27,768 --> 00:03:29,002
- HE TRULY IS A DEMON.

18
00:03:29,035 --> 00:03:32,602
- EVERY WOMAN THE CHIEF HAS HAD
ALWAYS DISAPPEARED MYSTERIOUSLY.

19
00:03:32,635 --> 00:03:35,068
THIS EXPLAINS
WHAT HAPPENED TO THEM.

20
00:03:35,102 --> 00:03:36,302
- CURSE HIM.

21
00:03:36,335 --> 00:03:37,768
LEAVE THEM ALONE!

22
00:03:37,802 --> 00:03:40,202
[GRUNTING]

23
00:03:40,235 --> 00:03:42,302
- INUYASHA,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

24
00:03:42,335 --> 00:03:43,635
HANG ON.

25
00:03:43,668 --> 00:03:44,568
[LAUGHS]

26
00:03:44,602 --> 00:03:48,068
- THE POISON HAS SPREAD
THROUGHOUT HIS BODY.

27
00:03:48,102 --> 00:03:49,002
[SCREAMING]

28
00:03:49,035 --> 00:03:53,102
- OBSERVE ME UNTIL YOU PERISH,
HALF-DEMON,

29
00:03:53,135 --> 00:03:57,002
AS I DEVOUR THESE WOMEN
ONE BY ONE.

30
00:04:08,102 --> 00:04:10,668
- IF I CAN GET THIS SWORD
TO HIM,

31
00:04:10,702 --> 00:04:13,435
WE WILL ALL BE SAVED.

32
00:04:15,302 --> 00:04:16,702
- HUH?

33
00:04:16,735 --> 00:04:18,068
MY SWORD!

34
00:04:18,102 --> 00:04:19,302
- THE TETSUSAIGA.

35
00:04:19,335 --> 00:04:20,602
- YOU MUST USE THE SWORD

36
00:04:20,635 --> 00:04:24,235
AND SAVE OUR WOMEN
FROM THIS TERRIBLE FATE!

37
00:04:24,268 --> 00:04:28,102
- WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING?

38
00:04:28,135 --> 00:04:30,768
STUPID OLD FOOL.

39
00:04:31,368 --> 00:04:35,268
YOU'VE SEALED YOUR OWN FATE
THIS TIME.

40
00:04:38,035 --> 00:04:39,768
- DAMN THEM.

41
00:04:41,102 --> 00:04:45,868
- THAT'LL TEACH YOU
FOR TRYING TO ACT SMART,
YOU OLD GEEZER.

42
00:04:45,902 --> 00:04:47,268
- GRANDPA!

43
00:04:47,302 --> 00:04:48,902
- HUH?

44
00:04:48,935 --> 00:04:51,202
[CRYING]

45
00:04:51,235 --> 00:04:52,802
- GRAMPS.

46
00:04:52,835 --> 00:04:55,935
- HUH, ANOTHER NUISANCE.

47
00:05:00,835 --> 00:05:02,435
- ARE YOU OK?

48
00:05:02,468 --> 00:05:03,535
- THE SWORD.

49
00:05:03,568 --> 00:05:05,035
- HUH?

50
00:05:05,902 --> 00:05:09,702
- GIVE THE SWORD
TO YOUR FRIEND.

51
00:05:10,368 --> 00:05:11,835
- THE TETSUSAIGA?

52
00:05:11,868 --> 00:05:14,035
WHERE'S INUYASHA?

53
00:05:14,068 --> 00:05:14,935
WHERE?

54
00:05:14,968 --> 00:05:16,535
IS HE HERE?

55
00:05:18,068 --> 00:05:21,868
- AH, A DELECTABLE-LOOKING
WOMAN.

56
00:05:21,902 --> 00:05:23,202
BRING HER TO ME.

57
00:05:23,235 --> 00:05:24,135
- SIR.

58
00:05:24,168 --> 00:05:25,402
[LAUGHING]

59
00:05:25,435 --> 00:05:27,868
- WHY, YOU...

60
00:05:27,902 --> 00:05:29,568
- COME QUIETLY.

61
00:05:29,602 --> 00:05:32,668
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
INUYASHA?

62
00:05:32,702 --> 00:05:33,668
[GASPS]

63
00:05:33,702 --> 00:05:34,368
OH, NO.

64
00:05:34,402 --> 00:05:36,535
THE BARRIER'S DIMINISHING.

65
00:05:46,035 --> 00:05:47,435
- WHAT DO YOU WANT WITH HER?

66
00:05:47,468 --> 00:05:49,635
- WE'RE FOLLOWING
THE CHIEF'S ORDERS.

67
00:05:49,668 --> 00:05:51,635
HAND THE GIRL OVER.

68
00:05:51,668 --> 00:05:52,502
- NO WAY!

69
00:05:52,535 --> 00:05:55,535
YOU WON'T TOUCH A HAIR
ON KAGOME'S HEAD!

70
00:05:57,202 --> 00:05:58,035
- SANGO!

71
00:05:58,068 --> 00:05:59,502
- YOU AIN'T GETTING AWAY.

72
00:05:59,535 --> 00:06:01,302
- THERE'S TOO MANY OF THEM.

73
00:06:01,335 --> 00:06:02,868
- GET HER!

74
00:06:05,002 --> 00:06:05,868
- IT'S BREAKING.

75
00:06:05,902 --> 00:06:09,268
THE BARRIER WON'T HOLD OUT
MUCH LONGER.

76
00:06:09,302 --> 00:06:12,102
INUYASHA, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

77
00:06:12,135 --> 00:06:13,802
HANG ON.

78
00:06:17,402 --> 00:06:20,968
[SCREAMING]

79
00:06:22,935 --> 00:06:24,435
INUYASHA?

80
00:06:24,468 --> 00:06:26,635
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

81
00:06:33,168 --> 00:06:35,135
- WHAT'S THIS?!

82
00:06:40,568 --> 00:06:41,368
- INUYASHA.

83
00:06:41,402 --> 00:06:44,635
- HE RIPPED THROUGH
MY POISON COCOON.

84
00:07:04,835 --> 00:07:06,735
- INUYASHA.

85
00:07:20,535 --> 00:07:21,368
- OH, NO!

86
00:07:21,402 --> 00:07:22,335
LOOK AT HIS FACE!

87
00:07:22,368 --> 00:07:24,402
- HE'S TRANSFORMED.

88
00:07:28,335 --> 00:07:32,235
- YOU AMUSE ME,
BUT THE SHOW IS OVER.

89
00:07:36,568 --> 00:07:39,235
YOU ARE NO MORE
THAN A HALF-DEMON.

90
00:07:39,268 --> 00:07:44,902
YOU CANNOT DEFEAT ME,
THE DEMON KATENMARU.

91
00:07:46,768 --> 00:07:49,402
DIE, LITTLE MAN.

92
00:08:08,435 --> 00:08:12,835
WHY DOES HE CARRY THE SCENT
OF PURE DEMON BLOOD?

93
00:08:19,735 --> 00:08:20,968
I MELTED HIM!

94
00:08:21,002 --> 00:08:23,102
HE WAS MERELY A HALF-DEMON.

95
00:08:23,135 --> 00:08:24,835
- YOU TALKING TO ME?

96
00:08:24,868 --> 00:08:27,002
- HUH?

97
00:08:27,035 --> 00:08:29,835
- FILTHY VERMIN!

98
00:08:46,168 --> 00:08:48,168
YOU WON'T ESCAPE.

99
00:08:50,602 --> 00:08:52,502
- INUYASHA.

100
00:08:55,168 --> 00:08:58,268
- LORD SESSHOMARU.

101
00:08:58,302 --> 00:08:59,668
OH, LORD SESSHOMARU,

102
00:08:59,702 --> 00:09:02,502
HAVE YOU GONE AWAY
AND LEFT ME ONCE AGAIN?

103
00:09:02,535 --> 00:09:06,702
LORD SESSHOMARU,
WHERE ARE YOU, MASTER?

104
00:09:06,735 --> 00:09:09,202
LORD SESSHOMARU,
HOW COULD YOU LEAVE

105
00:09:09,235 --> 00:09:14,068
WITHOUT TAKING
YOUR FAITHFUL RETAINER
ALONG WITH YOU?!

106
00:09:14,102 --> 00:09:15,202
I KNOW.

107
00:09:15,235 --> 00:09:18,735
IT'S ALL BECAUSE OF YOU, RIN.

108
00:09:18,768 --> 00:09:19,968
CURSES!

109
00:09:20,002 --> 00:09:23,802
OH, I SURE WISH
HE WOULD ABANDON THAT
HUMAN CHILD SOMEWHERE.

110
00:09:23,835 --> 00:09:24,968
AH!

111
00:09:25,002 --> 00:09:26,135
WAIT A MINUTE.

112
00:09:26,168 --> 00:09:29,035
COULD IT BE THAT
LORD SESSHOMARU IS GONE
TO FIND INUYASHA

113
00:09:29,068 --> 00:09:33,102
IN ORDER TO CONFIRM
WHAT BOKUSENO ADVISED HIM?

114
00:09:33,135 --> 00:09:33,868
- HUH?

115
00:09:33,902 --> 00:09:35,702
WHAT IS THIS INUYASHA LIKE,
JAKEN?

116
00:09:35,735 --> 00:09:38,235
- AN EXCELLENT QUESTION, RIN.

117
00:09:38,268 --> 00:09:39,835
IT'S A LONG STORY,

118
00:09:39,868 --> 00:09:42,268
BUT ONE WHICH MUST BE CONVEYED.

119
00:09:42,302 --> 00:09:44,235
[CLEARS THROAT]

120
00:09:44,268 --> 00:09:45,368
AS YOU ARE AWARE,

121
00:09:45,402 --> 00:09:49,535
INUYASHA IS LORD SESSHOMARU'S
YOUNGER BROTHER,

122
00:09:49,568 --> 00:09:52,202
BUT HE HARDLY COMPARES
IN DEMON RANK

123
00:09:52,235 --> 00:09:53,902
OR IN DEMON DIGNITY,

124
00:09:53,935 --> 00:09:56,368
AND THAT IS BECAUSE HE IS--

125
00:09:56,402 --> 00:09:58,768
HUH? HMM?

126
00:10:02,935 --> 00:10:03,702
HOLD UP!

127
00:10:03,735 --> 00:10:04,568
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

128
00:10:04,602 --> 00:10:08,102
- OH, I DON'T REALLY LIKE
LONG STORIES.

129
00:10:09,068 --> 00:10:10,402
LET'S GO, AH AND UN.

130
00:10:10,435 --> 00:10:13,102
WE'LL FIND SOME NICE,
JUICY GRASS.

131
00:10:15,268 --> 00:10:18,935
- I JUST WANTED
TO TELL THE STORY.

132
00:10:19,868 --> 00:10:22,435
[SCREAMING]

133
00:10:24,535 --> 00:10:26,935
- YOU WON'T GET AWAY.

134
00:11:06,002 --> 00:11:08,135
- KAGOME!

135
00:11:08,168 --> 00:11:12,035
- KILALA, STAY HERE
AND PROTECT THE VILLAGERS.

136
00:11:14,635 --> 00:11:16,535
- INUYASHA!

137
00:11:23,768 --> 00:11:24,968
- I BEG YOU TO SPARE US.

138
00:11:25,002 --> 00:11:28,602
- WE WERE SIMPLY FOLLOWING
THE CHIEF'S ORDERS.

139
00:11:28,635 --> 00:11:29,468
THAT'S ALL.

140
00:11:29,502 --> 00:11:30,735
- HAVE MERCY ON US.

141
00:11:30,768 --> 00:11:32,602
- DON'T DO IT, INUYASHA!

142
00:11:32,635 --> 00:11:35,202
THEY'RE BEGGING FOR THEIR LIVES!

143
00:11:37,502 --> 00:11:41,202
- IT SEEMS NOT EVEN YOU
CAN GET THROUGH TO HIM, KAGOME.

144
00:11:41,235 --> 00:11:42,802
- HUH.

145
00:11:42,835 --> 00:11:45,868
[LAUGHING]

146
00:11:48,402 --> 00:11:49,368
- HE'S LAUGHING.

147
00:11:49,402 --> 00:11:53,935
HE'S ABOUT TO SLAUGHTER THEM,
AND HE'S LAUGHING.

148
00:11:53,968 --> 00:11:56,335
- KAGOME, GIVE TETSUSAIGA
TO INUYASHA,

149
00:11:56,368 --> 00:11:57,635
AND HE'LL RETURN TO NORMAL.

150
00:11:57,668 --> 00:12:01,702
I CAN'T STAND TO SEE
WHAT HE'S TURNED INTO NOW.

151
00:12:02,835 --> 00:12:06,135
- INUYASHA,
TAKE THE TETSUSAIGA.

152
00:12:06,968 --> 00:12:10,468
RETURN TO YOUR OLD SELF,
INUYASHA.

153
00:12:22,868 --> 00:12:24,102
- SESSHOMARU!

154
00:12:24,135 --> 00:12:26,468
- WHY IS HE HERE?

155
00:12:37,668 --> 00:12:38,568
- HMM.

156
00:12:38,602 --> 00:12:41,902
YOU ARE NOTHING MORE
THAN A MURDEROUS DEMON.

157
00:12:41,935 --> 00:12:44,268
- UNFORTUNATELY FOR INUYASHA,

158
00:12:44,302 --> 00:12:46,235
THE PURE DEMON BLOOD
OF HIS FATHER

159
00:12:46,268 --> 00:12:49,768
IS TOO STRONG FOR A HALF-DEMON
SUCH AS HIMSELF.

160
00:12:49,802 --> 00:12:53,468
IN ESSENCE,
THE DEMON BLOOD
WILL ATTACK THE SOUL.

161
00:12:53,502 --> 00:12:57,468
HE WILL NOT BE ABLE
TO RECOGNIZE HIMSELF.

162
00:13:05,435 --> 00:13:08,435
- COME AFTER ME, INUYASHA.

163
00:13:08,468 --> 00:13:13,068
I WISH TO TEST YOUR STRENGTH,
TRANSFORMED AS SUCH.

164
00:13:31,835 --> 00:13:33,035
- INUYASHA!

165
00:13:33,068 --> 00:13:34,435
- NO! DON'T DO IT!

166
00:13:34,468 --> 00:13:37,035
SESSHOMARU'S NEW SWORD
CAN SLAY AN ENEMY

167
00:13:37,068 --> 00:13:38,468
WITH THE SLIGHTEST
BIT OF PRESSURE!

168
00:13:38,502 --> 00:13:42,735
YOU'LL BE DESTROYED
BEFORE YOU EVEN
GET CLOSE TO HIM!

169
00:13:47,868 --> 00:13:51,068
- HE FOUGHT OFF
SESSHOMARU'S SWORD.

170
00:13:55,635 --> 00:13:58,235
- HUH, THAT WAS FOOLISH.

171
00:14:13,302 --> 00:14:15,168
- HE'S CUT ALL OVER.

172
00:14:15,202 --> 00:14:16,602
- STOP ALREADY!

173
00:14:16,635 --> 00:14:18,102
INUYASHA!

174
00:14:18,135 --> 00:14:21,468
- INUYASHA, YOU FEEL NO FEAR.

175
00:14:21,502 --> 00:14:23,135
YOU KNOW NO PAIN.

176
00:14:23,168 --> 00:14:26,168
THE DEMON BLOOD
COURSING THROUGH YOUR VEINS

177
00:14:26,202 --> 00:14:28,002
HAS TAKEN OVER YOUR SOUL.

178
00:14:28,035 --> 00:14:30,302
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHO YOU ARE,

179
00:14:30,335 --> 00:14:35,168
AND YOU WILL CONTINUE FIGHTING
UNTIL YOU DIE.

180
00:14:37,535 --> 00:14:43,735
I CAME IN YOUR PURSUIT
TO SEE IF BOKUSENO'S
WORDS WERE TRUE.

181
00:14:43,768 --> 00:14:48,002
AND NOW, LITTLE BROTHER,
I UNDERSTAND.

182
00:14:50,502 --> 00:14:53,135
YOU ARE NOT
A FULL-FLEDGED DEMON.

183
00:14:53,168 --> 00:14:56,002
ALL YOU ARE IS A HALF-BREED.

184
00:14:58,968 --> 00:15:02,268
KNOW YOUR PLACE IN THE WORLD.

185
00:15:02,302 --> 00:15:06,302
A HALF-DEMON
SHOULD ACT LIKE ONE.

186
00:15:06,335 --> 00:15:08,435
ON YOUR KNEES.

187
00:15:28,868 --> 00:15:30,568
- INUYASHA!

188
00:15:41,256 --> 00:15:43,323
- INUYASHA!

189
00:15:49,289 --> 00:15:51,323
INUYASHA!

190
00:16:03,423 --> 00:16:05,156
PLEASE STOP.

191
00:16:08,756 --> 00:16:11,756
- HE HAS FINALLY
BEEN BROUGHT DOWN.

192
00:16:13,156 --> 00:16:15,123
- DON'T COME ANY NEARER.

193
00:16:15,156 --> 00:16:16,323
- KAGOME, NO!

194
00:16:16,356 --> 00:16:18,589
- KAGOME'S IN TROUBLE!

195
00:16:26,289 --> 00:16:27,523
- IF YOU WISH HIM TO STOP,

196
00:16:27,556 --> 00:16:30,723
USE TETSUSAIGA TO REVERSE
THE TRANSFORMATION.

197
00:16:30,756 --> 00:16:32,523
[GASPS]

198
00:16:32,556 --> 00:16:35,789
OTHERWISE,
HE WILL CONTINUE TO FIGHT
WHEN HE AWAKENS.

199
00:16:35,823 --> 00:16:39,589
- I THOUGHT HE WANTED
TO KILL INUYASHA.

200
00:16:41,456 --> 00:16:44,323
- YOU COULD HAVE
FINISHED HIM OFF EARLIER
IF YOU WANTED TO.

201
00:16:44,356 --> 00:16:47,756
INSTEAD YOU MERELY HELD HIM OFF
WITH YOUR SWORD.

202
00:16:49,289 --> 00:16:51,056
WHY DID YOU STOP AT THAT?

203
00:16:51,089 --> 00:16:52,889
WE ALL KNOW
YOU DESPISE INUYASHA.

204
00:16:52,923 --> 00:16:57,023
I CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU'VE DEVELOPED FEELINGS
FOR YOUR BROTHER.

205
00:16:57,056 --> 00:17:00,023
- I WILL SLAY HIM EVENTUALLY.

206
00:17:00,056 --> 00:17:03,623
WHY KILL HIM NOW
WHEN HE DOESN'T KNOW HIMSELF?

207
00:17:03,656 --> 00:17:06,089
THERE WOULD BE NO POINT.

208
00:17:12,623 --> 00:17:17,956
- IT'S ALMOST AS IF
HE CAME TO STOP
INUYASHA'S VIOLENT BEHAVIOR.

209
00:17:17,989 --> 00:17:20,523
[MOANING]

210
00:17:22,289 --> 00:17:23,356
- INUYASHA.

211
00:17:23,389 --> 00:17:25,356
- HE'S COME TO.

212
00:17:35,723 --> 00:17:40,656
- OH, LORD SESSHOMARU,
YOU'RE FINALLY BACK.

213
00:17:40,689 --> 00:17:43,289
- RIN, I HOPE
YOU HAVE FARED WELL.

214
00:17:43,323 --> 00:17:44,289
- MM-HMM.

215
00:17:44,323 --> 00:17:46,889
AH AND UN AND I WERE ON
OUR VERY BEST BEHAVIOR.

216
00:17:46,923 --> 00:17:50,523
JAKEN HAS BECOME
MOST MELANCHOLY, THOUGH.

217
00:17:54,189 --> 00:17:57,123
- LORD SESSHOMARU!

218
00:17:57,156 --> 00:17:58,789
WHAT GIVES, MILORD?

219
00:17:58,823 --> 00:18:02,189
WHY DID YOU GO ALONE
AFTER INUYASHA?

220
00:18:05,256 --> 00:18:08,123
MASTER,
THAT WAS MOST UNCALLED FOR.

221
00:18:08,156 --> 00:18:10,456
I HOPE YOU CAN FORGIVE ME.

222
00:18:13,656 --> 00:18:14,756
- HMM?

223
00:18:14,789 --> 00:18:17,456
- LORD SESSHOMARU?

224
00:18:25,856 --> 00:18:29,123
- INUYASHA,
YOU SHOULDN'T BE MOVING YET.

225
00:18:29,756 --> 00:18:31,256
- DID I DO ALL THIS?

226
00:18:31,289 --> 00:18:32,789
[GASPS]

227
00:18:34,056 --> 00:18:36,123
- DOESN'T HE REMEMBER?

228
00:18:36,956 --> 00:18:38,589
- HUH, LOOK AT ME.

229
00:18:38,623 --> 00:18:44,789
MY CLAWS ABSOLUTELY
REEK OF THE SCENT
OF THE BANDITS' BLOOD.

230
00:18:45,823 --> 00:18:47,456
- THE POOR GUY.

231
00:18:47,489 --> 00:18:51,789
INUYASHA, YOU DID IT
TO SAVE THE INNOCENT.

232
00:18:52,389 --> 00:18:55,623
THAT'S WHY
YOU ATTACKED THESE BANDITS.

233
00:19:04,689 --> 00:19:06,023
- NO. HE'S A DEMON.

234
00:19:06,056 --> 00:19:09,389
- IF YOU GET CLOSE,
HE'LL RIP YOU TO PIECES.

235
00:19:11,256 --> 00:19:13,056
- YOU'RE WRONG.

236
00:19:25,423 --> 00:19:27,089
- I DON'T CARE
IF HE IS A DEMON!

237
00:19:27,123 --> 00:19:30,456
HE DID EVERYTHING IN HIS POWER
TO SAVE MY GRANDPA!

238
00:19:30,489 --> 00:19:33,556
HE HELPED GET RID
OF ALL THE BAD MEN!

239
00:19:39,089 --> 00:19:40,256
- NO.

240
00:19:40,289 --> 00:19:43,023
I HUNTED THOSE MEN DOWN.

241
00:19:43,056 --> 00:19:45,556
THE DEMON
THAT I WANTED TO BECOME,

242
00:19:45,589 --> 00:19:47,656
THE POWER THAT I DESIRED,

243
00:19:47,689 --> 00:19:50,723
IT WASN'T LIKE THIS.

244
00:19:56,011 --> 00:19:59,311
- EACH TIME INUYASHA
TRANSFORMS INTO A DEMON,

245
00:19:59,345 --> 00:20:00,845
HE LOSES A PIECE OF HIMSELF.

246
00:20:00,878 --> 00:20:03,911
TODAY HE DIDN'T EVEN HEAR
KAGOME'S VOICE.

247
00:20:03,945 --> 00:20:06,845
- MIROKU, I WANT TO STAY
WITH INUYASHA,

248
00:20:06,878 --> 00:20:10,345
EVEN IF HE FULLY TRANSFORMS
INTO A DEMON.

249
00:20:11,511 --> 00:20:12,311
- SANGO.

250
00:20:12,345 --> 00:20:14,845
- I CAUSED SO MUCH TROUBLE
OVER KOHAKU,

251
00:20:14,878 --> 00:20:16,278
BUT YOU'VE ALL STOOD BY ME

252
00:20:16,311 --> 00:20:18,445
LIKE IT WAS
THE NATURAL THING TO DO.

253
00:20:18,478 --> 00:20:21,511
THAT'S WHY I MUST STAND
BEHIND HIM.

254
00:20:26,045 --> 00:20:27,678
- YES.

255
00:20:43,311 --> 00:20:46,678
- I CAN'T GET THE SMELL OF BLOOD
OFF MY HANDS!

256
00:20:46,711 --> 00:20:48,845
IT'S SICKENING!

257
00:21:04,778 --> 00:21:05,711
- HERE.

258
00:21:05,745 --> 00:21:07,445
- KEEP IT.

259
00:21:15,911 --> 00:21:19,778
YOU DON'T HAVE TO FORCE YOURSELF
TO STAY BY ME.

260
00:21:25,078 --> 00:21:26,211
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM?

261
00:21:26,245 --> 00:21:29,311
YOU KNOW,
I WISH YOU'D ALL STOP
PUSSYFOOTING AROUND ME,

262
00:21:29,345 --> 00:21:32,611
BECAUSE I DON'T HAVE A PROBLEM
WITH WHAT HAPPENED.

263
00:21:32,645 --> 00:21:34,845
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN
WHAT I DID!

264
00:21:34,878 --> 00:21:37,111
- DON'T KID YOURSELF.

265
00:21:40,811 --> 00:21:43,778
IT MUST BE SO HARD ON HIM.

266
00:21:46,478 --> 00:21:47,945
- HUH?

267
00:21:48,911 --> 00:21:52,945
- OH, INUYASHA,
I KNOW HOW YOU FEEL.

268
00:21:53,778 --> 00:21:56,911
- KAGOME,
I DON'T REMEMBER A THING

269
00:21:56,945 --> 00:21:59,578
FROM WHEN I WAS TRANSFORMED.

270
00:21:59,611 --> 00:22:02,445
IT WASN'T LIKE THAT BEFORE.

271
00:22:02,478 --> 00:22:04,545
THE NEXT TIME I TRANSFORM,

272
00:22:04,578 --> 00:22:08,878
I MAY EVEN COME AFTER YOU
WITH THESE CLAWS, KAGOME.

273
00:22:30,317 --> 00:22:33,050
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

274
00:23:59,006 --> 00:24:02,006
- INUYASHA CAN'T SUPPRESS
HIS VIOLENT DEMON BLOOD,

275
00:24:02,039 --> 00:24:05,106
BUT HE DOESN'T WANT TO BECOME
A MURDEROUS DEMON.

276
00:24:05,139 --> 00:24:06,706
THERE MUST BE A SOLUTION.

277
00:24:06,739 --> 00:24:08,406
IF HE DEFEATS RYUKOTSUSEI,

278
00:24:08,439 --> 00:24:09,872
TETSUSAIGA
WILL BECOME LIGHTER

279
00:24:09,906 --> 00:24:12,272
AND EASIER
FOR INUYASHA TO WIELD.

280
00:24:12,306 --> 00:24:15,406
RELUCTANTLY,
HE OBEYS TOTOSAI'S ADVICE.

281
00:24:15,439 --> 00:24:19,539
MEANWHILE,
NARAKU IS UP TO NO GOOD AGAIN.

282
00:24:20,472 --> 00:24:24,406
NEXT TIME...

283
00:24:24,439 --> 00:24:25,439
SEE YOU SOON.

